channel.title: PkScape[317] for beginners
channel.description:
Hey Moparscapians!
This is my source which I've worked on for a while (like 3 weeks :p)
It's Delta based (fuck off if you don't like it).
I made this for a re-make of a server I used to play, that's why I got into servers.
[b]Some features of PkScape v1.0[/b]
[ul]Real DDS specs like RS.
[list][li]Stable godwars and economy[/li]
[li]People star(ed) making money by alching *50k an alch*[/li]
[li]Stable XP, no too fast but not too slow[/li]
[li]Rune Knifes fixed (needs a bit of tuning up)[/li]
[li]Turmoil (ghetto, tooltips in client are fucked) and Piety with real RS affects (could use some tuning up on Turmoil)[/li]
[li]Old school, so no 500+ shit loaded into it (except some gfx and emotes) but you have to find them out your self[/li]
[/list] More added, find out when you download this
MEDIA: [img]http://img143.imageshack.us/img143/8330/59115748.png[/img] [img]http://img168.imageshack.us/img168/7428/42800144.png[/img] [img]http://img97.imageshack.us/img97/4467/48846116.png[/img]
this is for starters and people wanting to learn the basics of server programming, etc.
Nonetheless, [url=http://uppit.com/v/TIFFBF4C]here's[/url] the download
**Remember anyone who is more advanced into programming, this is for newbies**
CREDITS: 80% Delta_ for the Source and Client 15% Tuts from R-S for client stuff 5% me for adding it and making a basic server.
Please don't flame and be like "OMDOMGOM LOLOLLOL111!!!!11!!!@!@ D3LT@ L33CHERZ!@ LOLULUILOL U SAWK L3C0DE NOUOB!!11" I made this for the people just starting.
Thanks for viewing.
Also, if you download it and are nice, make some download mirrors, it will help people :p
Also...
search for[/ul] [code]"the owner[/code] in client.java, to the left of that there's like "gaysexy or something, remove that.
